      "description": "<p><strong>Max Ranks</strong>: 5</p><ul><li><p>An Envenomed creature or object takes 1d6 poison damage for each rank it has, at the start of each of their turns for the duration of this condition</p></li><li><p>An Envenomed creature suffers a -1 penalty to their AC for each rank it has. </p></li><li><p>An Envenomed creature cannot gain the benefits of a rest. </p></li><li><p>Creatures that are immune to poison damage are immune to the envenomed condition. </p></li><li><p>Outside of combat, every hour a creature suffers the effects of this condition as if a turn has passed in combat.</p></li></ul>",
